summary: Finally I have in my hands the second book of @laura_lp21 ✨✨ this is my favorite of all the books I have illustrated, I’m so...
body: Finally I have in my hands the second book of @laura_lp21 ✨✨ this is my favorite of all the books I have illustrated, I’m so happy with how it looks 😭💕💞 and also this is a special book for me, I worked on it while I was living in Kyoto, and I can remember with each of them were I was while drawing them 💕💕 if you buy the book, you can pay attention to the illustrations and find a lot of details of the things I like and my life, for example, one thing nobody knows, in the story, Laura’s grandma gave her a very special necklace for her, I ask the editorial if there was an specific design for that necklace and they told me to draw whatever I want, so the necklace that appears in the two books is the same one my grandma gave to me when I was young, she is gone now, but I love that I was able to put a little bit of her in the two books 💞(you can see the necklace in the 5th picture) You can find the book in Spain or buy it on Amazon 💞💞 is called Follow your dreams ✨✨✌🏻
